OL,5,G2315 John Denver: Rocky Mountain High:
OL,6,G     Live In Japan
OL,7,     FIn this 1981 concert, the folk
OL,8,     Frock legend performs his greatest
OL,9,     Fhits, including Annie's Song,
OL,10,     FCalypso and Sunshine on my
OL,11,     FShoulders.
OL,12,G0030 The Thousand And One Musical Lives
OL,13,G     of Fleetwood Mac
OL,14,     FExtraordinary musical longevity,
OL,15,     Ffuelled by the genius of its
OL,16,     Fperformers but also by numerous
OL,17,     Fabuses. Forty years of sex, drugs,
OL,18,     Fand rock'n'roll.
